This library (bytestring-show) contains some code adapted from other works.

  * Printing of various primitive values is adapted largely from the base
    libraries distributed with GHC. The GHC license will be reproduced
    below.

  * Decoding of characters into Word8s according to UTF-8 was
    borrowed from utf8-string, which is (c) Eric Mertens.

  * Significant modifications and original code have been written by
    Dan Doel.

